playstore_details.title: Lumi Collect - ERC721 Wallet&ETH dapp browser
playstore_details.description:
Lumi Collect is a smooth, easy and nice client-side Ethereum wallet that supports ERC721 tokens - your collectibles.
 

Like coins or tokens, all the collectibles are to be held in a wallet. For now, most owners of crypto collectibles use Metamask digital wallet, it is functioning as a bank account. 
Lumi Collect wallet takes care of its users and wants to broaden your horizons. 
So, Lumi Collect is like Metamask, but for mobile devices (IOS/Android apps), and it can sign any Dapp transactions with our in-app browser. 

Lumi Collect wallet gives you the opportunity to:
-  Collect crypto ERC721 tokens such as CryptoKitties, Blockchain Cuties and 0xUniverse there. We have created beautiful profile cards so you can enjoy your collectibles at 100 percent!
- Use the Dapp browser built right into the app.
- Use your favorite Ethereum sidechain.
- Add your Ethereum sidechain merely by 2 clicks. We support all ETH sidechains!


Lumi Collect main values:

LUMI - EXTREMELY SECURE 
Private keys are under client control, they are NEVER sent to anywhere or stored outside your device. 

LUMI - TOTALLY ANONYMOUS
There is no need to provide any personal information and no registration is required. Your privacy is essential to us.

LUMI - FROM PLAYERS TO PLAYERS
All our team is truly committed to developing one of the first high-class crypto wallets that will let you store & manage all your preferred collectibles. 

So, discover all the beauty of the decentralized world with Lumi Collect!
